  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A gazette from President Gota",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has issued a special gazette notice appointing Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe to oversee the work of the presidency with effect from today (13).",
        "It has been stated that this appointment will be made in accordance with the powers assigned by the constitution to act during that period as he cannot exercise the powers, functions and duties of the presidency during his absence from Sri Lanka."
      ],
